      <title>最高法院对 Nvidia 股东案的广泛裁决持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/supreme-court-wary-of-broad-ruling-in-nvidia-shareholder-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院法官表示，他们正考虑对英伟达公司提起诉讼，指控其在对加密挖矿收入的依赖上误导投资者，他们正朝着对股东诉讼做出狭隘裁决的方向前进。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/supreme-court-wary-of-broad-ruling-in-nvidia-shareholder-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 17:26:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
